haus_tips_content:
Guests can receive ONLY Common Sneakers. Buddies can receive Sneakers of ANY Quality.
A Guest‚Äôs daily energy consumption is directly deducted from the Host‚Äôs total Energy Pool.
The Host MUST consume a minimum of 2 Energy daily in order to collect earnings from the Haus.
One Activation Code can be generated for every 10 Energy consumed by the Host.
One Mint Quota can be generated for every 15 Energy consumed by everyone in the Haus.
Each Haus can accommodate up to five Guests.
